Makin' a withdrawal.

16
00:05:13,290 --> 00:05:15,330
‎今天要取多少钱
And, uh, how much will you be taking out today?

17
00:05:15,410 --> 00:05:16,540
‎有多少取多少
Ah, whatever's in there.

18
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,000
