we cannot bring an end to the Persian Gulf War.

22
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,040
‎没有伊朗的…
Without Iran's…

23
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:30,410
‎那…是很大一笔钱呢
-There's a lot of money.

24
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:32,620
‎我知道啊
I know.

25
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:34,620
‎钱就是我存进去的
I'm the one who put it in there.

26
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:49,500
‎如果您想打电话 ‎请先投币25美分 然后再拨号
If you'd like to place a call, please deposit 25 cents before dialing.

27
00:05:49,580 --> 00:05:53,160
‎如需帮助 请挂断后重新致电
If you need help, please hang up and try your call again.

28
00:05:59,290 --> 00:06:00,450
‎兰金
Rankin.

29
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:01,700
‎下午好 卢
Afternoon, Lou.

30
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:04,080
‎贾克斯心情很好嘛
Jax is in a good mood.

31
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,790
‎我不禁在想 ‎是不是因为打猎很刺激
Can't help but wonder if the spark of the hunt

32
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:08,330
‎所以才让它兴奋得不行
hasn't got him all worked up.

33
00:06:08,410 --> 00:06:10,500
‎不太可能 现在不是打猎的季节
Unlikely. It isn't hunting season.

34
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,830
‎哦
Oh.

35
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,250
‎那鹿一定是突然冒出来的
Deer must have just bolted out of nowhere.

36
00:06:17,330 --> 00:06:18,410
‎迅雷不及掩耳
Happened so fast.

37
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,950
‎我很高兴你和贾克斯安全出来了
Well, I'm glad you and Jax came out of it okay.

38
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,700
‎你应该给自己买一条铜手链
You know, you ought to get yourself one of these copper bracelets.

39
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:36,040
‎-漂亮 ‎-我侄女在大陆给我买的
-Pretty. -My niece got it for me on the mainland.

40
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:38,330
‎其中一个装着好梦安睡环
One of those stores, you know,

41
00:06:38,410 --> 00:06:40,040
‎还有水晶之类的东西
with the dream catchers and crystals and whatnot.

42
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:45,790
‎我还笑她来着 但我对天发誓 ‎现在我的关节炎好多了
-I laughed at her. But I swear to God, I barely feel the arthritis anymore.

43
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:47,200
‎我又开始钓鱼了
I'm fishin' again.

44
00:06:47,290 --> 00:06:49,750
‎戴着这玩意儿小心别被雷劈了
Careful you don't get struck by lightning wearin' that thing.

45
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:07,200
‎早上好 卢
-Oh, that's right. Mornin', Lou!

46
00:07:15,330 --> 00:07:16,250
‎我喜欢…
I love--

47
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:20,080
‎这是恶劣天气预警
This is a severe weather watch.

48
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:23,120
‎西北太平洋近年来最大的一次风暴
The biggest storm the Pacific Northwest has seen in years

49
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,660
‎预计将于今天入夜后来袭
is expected to make landfall early this evening.

50
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:28,080
‎请各位居民尽量待在家里
Residents are encouraged to stay in their homes

51
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:31,910
‎做好准备 届时会出现电力中断 ‎低洼地区会有洪涝
and be prepared for downed power lines and flooding in low-lying areas.

52
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:35,200
‎开往圣胡安群岛的渡轮也已暂停服务
Ferry service to the San Juan Islands has also been suspended

53
00:07:35,290 --> 00:07:36,660
‎重开时间另行通知
until further notice

54
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:39,580
‎因为风暴将直接吹袭本区域
as the area is directly in the storm's path.

55
00:07:47,910 --> 00:07:49,950
‎她跑哪儿去了呢 我不知道
Where could she be? I don't know.

56
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,620
‎她不在这棵树下
She's not under this tree.

57
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:53,580
‎（价真五金店）

58
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:55,040
‎她不在这里
She's not over here.

59
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,200
‎她藏得真好啊
Oh, she's so good at hiding.

60
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,250
‎一定得找到她
Gotta find her.

61
00:08:00,330 --> 00:08:01,830
‎也许她在里面
Maybe she's inside.

62
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,870
‎好 我去那里看看
Yeah, I'm gonna check there.

63
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:21,120
‎抓到你啦
-I got you! -I got you! I got you!

64
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:24,000
‎你都没有说“小兔子”的暗号
-You didn't say the code! Little Rabbit.

65
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:28,120
‎再来一次嘛
One more time.

66
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,120
‎不行
-No.

67
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,080
‎求你了
-Please.

68
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,160
‎我说了不行 小薇 来吧
I said no, Vee. Come on.

69
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:35,660
‎把钉子递给我
Pass me a nail?

70
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,080
‎谢谢
Thanks.

71
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:43,200
‎妈妈 你觉得 ‎爸爸会很快找到宝藏吗
Mom, do you think Daddy's gonna find the treasure soon?

72
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:45,080
‎已经两年了
It's been two years.

73
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:48,080
‎我不知道 小薇 他应该很快会找到的
I don't know, Vee. I bet he's real close.

74
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,750
‎那爸爸会回家吗
And then is Daddy gonna come home?

75
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:55,080
‎知道吗 风暴似乎还要过会儿才来
You know, the storm looks like it's a while away.

76
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,250
‎我们或许可以再玩一次躲猫猫
We could probably fit in another game.

77
00:08:57,330 --> 00:09:00,200
‎我打赌你撑不过三分钟 ‎就会被我找到了
I bet you can't make it past three minutes before I find you, though.

78
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:02,540
‎-我可以的 ‎-我觉得你撑不过
-Oh, I can. -Oh, I don't think you can.

79
00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:05,370
‎好吧 我看看 准备好了吗 预备…
All right. Let me see. Ready? Set…

80
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:07,120
‎-游戏开始 ‎-游戏开始
-Game on! -Game on!

81
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,410
‎一
One…

82
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,790
‎二
two…

83
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:11,080
‎三
three…

84
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:12,870
‎四
four…

85
00:09:13,950 --> 00:09:16,250
‎五 六
five… six…

86
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:18,950
‎七…
Seven…

87
00:09:36,450 --> 00:09:38,500
‎-嘿 卢 ‎-房租 明天
-Hey, Lou. -Rent. Tomorrow.

88
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:42,830
‎我知道 听我说 ‎我得为风暴准备食品物资
I know. Listen, now, I had to lay in supplies for the storm.

89
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:44,540
‎-能不能… ‎-不能延期
-So I was wondering whether-- -No extensions.

90
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:46,450
‎好吧
-All right.

91
00:09:46,540 --> 00:09:49,000
‎明天 把钱放在里面桌子上
-Tomorrow. Inside. On the table.

92
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:52,160
‎-不然放在信箱里会弄湿的 ‎-钱会付给你的
It'll get wet in the mailbox. You'll get it.

93
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,830
‎小薇
Vee!

94
00:10:29,540 --> 00:10:31,250
‎你这人是怎么回事
What the hell is wrong with you?

95
00:10:31,330 --> 00:10:33,910
‎明知道附近有小孩 ‎你为什么还要开这么快
Why you gotta drive so goddamn fast? You know there's a child nearby.

96
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:37,450
‎这世界不是游乐场 ‎教你的孩子要自己小心
World's not a playground. Teach your kid to look out for herself.

97
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:23,080
‎来吧 贾克斯
Come on, Jax.

98
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:30,620
‎-嘿 ‎-进去吧
-Hey. -Go inside.

99
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:32,450
‎-妈妈  ‎-小薇 进去吧
-No, Mom! -Vee, go inside.

100
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:34,450
‎没事吧
-Everything o-- okay?

101
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:38,000
‎别跺脚 小姑娘
And no stomping, little girl.

102
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:43,080
‎不 不用了 谢谢你 克里斯
-No. We're fine. Thanks, Chris.

103
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:46,120
‎-你还好吗  ‎-还好 我只是累了
-You doin' all right? -Yeah, I'm just tired.

104
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,290
好吧
All right.

105
00:11:47,370 --> 00:11:49,290
卢还在让你烦恼吗
Is Lou still bein' a pain in your ass?

106
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,540
‎我跟你说过这事
-I told you about that?

107
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:53,700
‎是啊
-Yeah.

108
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:56,370
‎-你不记得了 我们… ‎-不记得了
Yeah, you don't… you don't remember? -No.

109
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:59,160
‎听我说 我们当时都喝醉了
-Look, we were both pretty drunk, so…

110
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:00,750
‎-是啊 ‎-对 显然如此
-Yeah. Yeah. -Clearly,

111
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:02,750
‎因为我都不记得我说过了
'cause I… I don't remember that.

112
00:12:03,830 --> 00:12:06,950
‎我记得你使出了吃奶的劲儿 ‎在唱“宛如处女”
I do remember you singing "Like A Virgin" at the top of your lungs.

113
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:09,500
‎请你发誓不告诉别人
Oh, please swear you'll never tell.

114
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:11,750
‎不然呢
Or what?

115
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:13,540
‎我不知道
I don't know.

116
00:12:14,370 --> 00:12:15,500
‎不然…
Or, uh…

117
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:19,160
‎妈 我找不到河马先生
Mom! I can't find Mr. Hippo!

118
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:21,000
‎我得走了
Listen, I gotta go.

119
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,290
‎嘿 你有没有…
Hey, have you, um…

120
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:26,950
‎妈 帮我找把它找出来
-Mom, help me find him.

121
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:29,620
‎你找机会跟小薇谈过了吗
Have you had a chance to talk to Vee yet?

122
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:31,040
‎关于她爸的事
About her dad?

123
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:19,290
‎你没事吧
You all right?

124
00:13:19,370 --> 00:13:21,830
‎-我能搭个便车吗  ‎-当然可以 上车吧
-Any way I could get a ride? -Yeah, of course. Get in here. -Thank you.

125
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:31,120
‎倒霉的租赁车坏掉了 ‎你真是帮了我一个大忙
Sorry about that. Oh, damn rental car broke down on me. You're a lifesaver.

126
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:36,160
‎天啊 我把你的座位都弄湿了
Oh, jeez, I'm-- I'm gettin' your seat all soaked.

127
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:38,750
‎别担心 得亏是我开车经过看见了你
Don't worry about it, man. I'm just glad I passed you when I did.

128
00:13:39,410 --> 00:13:41,120
‎风暴天会很危险
The storm's gonna be gnarly.

129
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:01,950
‎（《论死亡与临终》）

130
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:03,750
‎好深奥啊
Heavy reading.

131
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:07,120
‎对 给我一个朋友买的
Yeah, I bought it for a friend of mine.

132
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:10,290
‎她的前夫三个月前去世了 ‎她很难接受现实 所以…
Her ex died three months ago, and she's just-- she's havin' a hard time facin' it.

133
00:14:10,370 --> 00:14:13,080
‎明白了 你想帮她面对现实吧
I see. And you wanna help her face it, right? Hm?

134
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:17,000
‎-因为你想比做朋友更进一步  ‎-不 听我说 我只是…她有个孩子
'Cause you wanna be more than just friends? Oh, look, I just-- She has a kid.

135
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:19,040
‎她想慢慢来
She wants to take it slow.

136
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:26,750
‎哦 我喜欢这个乐队
Oh! I love this band.

137
00:14:26,830 --> 00:14:29,620
‎-杰夫波卡罗是个很厉害的人 ‎-哦 是的 他是最棒的
Oh, Jeff Porcaro's the man. -Oh, yeah. He's the best.

138
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,500
‎搞什么 操
Fuck! What the fuck?

139
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:23,370
‎（大学资金）

140
00:16:35,290 --> 00:16:38,370
‎（爸爸 小薇）

141
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:43,410
‎小薇
Vee…

142
00:16:45,330 --> 00:16:46,500
‎小薇 看着我
Vee, look at me.

143
00:16:50,330 --> 00:16:52,870
‎你之前问过爸爸的事 对吧
You know when you were asking about Daddy earlier?

144
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,660
‎怎么说呢…
Well, um…

145
00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:02,160
‎宝贝 他…
Baby, he, um…

146
00:17:07,410 --> 00:17:09,950
‎他很爱你
He loves you so much.

147
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:14,040
‎他心里一直在挂念你
And he thinks about you all the time.

148
00:17:20,120 --> 00:17:21,290
‎你在做什么呢
What are we making?

149
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,870
‎-友谊手链 ‎-哦
-Friendship bracelets. -Oh.

150
00:17:23,950 --> 00:17:25,620
‎我想做一条友谊手链
I wanna make a friendship bracelet.

151
00:17:25,700 --> 00:17:27,160
‎这个是给卢的
This one is for Lou.

152
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:29,450
‎你在给卢做手链 为什么
You're making a bracelet for Lou? Why?

153
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:30,790
‎我喜欢卢
I like Lou.

154
00:17:31,660 --> 00:17:32,750
‎我知道你不喜欢
-I know you don't.

155
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:33,750
‎不 我喜欢啊
-Yeah, I do.

156
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:40,580
‎好吧 我其实不喜欢卢 ‎但是你为什么喜欢她呢
Okay. I actually don't like Lou. But why do you like her?

157
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:43,870
‎因为贾克斯喜欢她 而我喜欢贾克斯
Well, Jax likes her, and I like Jax.

158
00:17:43,950 --> 00:17:44,870
‎哦
Oh.

159
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:56,540
‎我向来不是话多的人 ‎我就长话短说了
"I've never been one for many words, so I'll keep this short."

160
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:59,660
‎房子归你了 拿去卖掉吧
"The house is yours. Sell it."

161
00:18:00,250 --> 00:18:04,370
‎冰箱的肉够贾克斯吃一个月 ‎还有给你一些现金
"There's a month's worth of meat for Jax in the freezer, and some cash for you."

162
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:10,160
‎我做的一些决定 你永远都不会理解
"There are certain decisions I made that you will never understand."

163
00:18:12,580 --> 00:18:14,700
‎但那都是过去的事了
"But that's all in the past now."

164
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,500
‎人生可能会很残酷
"Life can be cruel."

165
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:21,250
‎有些事我很擅长 ‎但有些事我做得一塌糊涂
"What made me great at some things made me lousy at others."

166
00:18:25,750 --> 00:18:29,410
‎我希望我能说 ‎自己的所作所为带来了好的结果
"I wish I could say that some good came from what I did."

167
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:31,370
‎事实上
"In truth,

168
00:18:32,370 --> 00:18:34,660
‎我让世界变成了更危险的地方
I left the world a more dangerous place."

169
00:18:49,830 --> 00:18:51,910
‎现在该睡啦 好了
-Bedtime, now!

170
00:18:53,950 --> 00:18:55,330
‎-河马先生  ‎-我累坏了
-Mr. Hippo! -I'm exhausted.

171
00:18:55,410 --> 00:18:57,500
‎来吧 河马先生 晚安
Come on, Mr. Hippo. -Good night.

172
00:18:57,580 --> 00:18:58,580
‎我好热
-I'm hot.

173
00:18:58,660 --> 00:19:02,330
‎我也很热 ‎但很快就凉快了 因为下雨了
Yeah, now I'm hot too. But you'll be cold soon because it's raining.

174
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:08,620
‎只是风而已 宝贝 别害怕
Oh, it's just the wind, baby. Don't be scared.

175
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:09,750
‎我没有怕
-I'm not scared.

176
00:19:10,290 --> 00:19:11,910
‎-好的 ‎-你害怕吗
-Okay. -Are you scared?

177
00:19:12,870 --> 00:19:15,830
‎-你今晚想跟我睡吗  ‎-如果你想 我就跟你睡
-Do you wanna sleep with me tonight? -Oh, if you need me to, I will.

178
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:17,200
‎我想让你跟我睡
-I think I do.

179
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,290
‎该死
Oh shit.

180
00:19:21,370 --> 00:19:23,040
‎该死
Shit, shit, shit, shit!

181
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:24,040
‎小薇
-Vee…

182
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:26,160
‎-说话注意点 ‎-该死
-Watch your mouth. -Shit!

183
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:33,370
‎我要去把断电器打上去
I'm just gonna go flip the breaker.

184
00:19:34,290 --> 00:19:35,450
‎我马上回来 好吗
I'll be right back, okay?

185
00:20:25,410 --> 00:20:26,500
‎妈妈
Mommy?

186
00:20:27,950 --> 00:20:29,160
‎是你吗
Is that you?

187
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:16,870
‎克里斯
Chris!

188
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:39,620
‎小薇
Oh! Vee!

189
00:21:45,120 --> 00:21:47,290
‎不 小薇
No! Vee!

190
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:51,540
‎小薇
Vee!

191
00:21:58,200 --> 00:22:01,500
‎小薇
Vee! Vee! Vee! Vee? Vee!

192
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:56,410
‎-电话呢  ‎-搞什么鬼
-Where's your phone? -What the hell?

193
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:59,660
‎该死的电话在哪 我得打给警长
Where's your goddamn phone? I gotta call the sheriff.

194
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:05,120
‎-妈的 操  ‎-别急 出什么事了
-God damn it! Fuck! -Slow down. What happened?

195
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,000
‎小薇不见了
-Vee's gone.

196
00:23:07,080 --> 00:23:09,500
‎你又让她跑开了 她走不了多远
-What, you let her wander off again? -She's not gonna get far in this.

197
00:23:09,580 --> 00:23:11,450
‎不 她爸爸把她带走了
-No, no, no. -Her father took her.

198
00:23:11,540 --> 00:23:12,620
‎她爸爸
-Her father?

199
00:23:13,910 --> 00:23:16,410
‎他来了 他怎么会在这里
He's… he's here. How the hell is he here?

200
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:18,290
‎等等 你看到他了吗
Hold on. You saw him?

201
00:23:18,370 --> 00:23:20,330
‎没有 我…
No. I…

202
00:23:20,410 --> 00:23:23,370
‎他应该是死了 但是他找到了我们
He… he's supposed to be dead, but he found us.

203
00:23:23,450 --> 00:23:25,160
‎我以为摆脱他了
I-- I thought we were free of him.

204
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,160
‎他还杀了克里斯
-He killed Chris.

205
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:28,120
‎天啊
-Jesus Christ.

206
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:32,450
‎你的钥匙呢  ‎车子发动不了 我得去找警长
Where are your keys? The car won't start. I gotta get to the sheriff.

207
00:23:32,540 --> 00:23:33,790
‎-我来开车 ‎-好
-I'll drive. -Okay.

208
00:23:40,910 --> 00:23:41,790
‎糟了
Hm.

209
00:23:42,580 --> 00:23:44,620
‎快点
-No, no, no, no, no! Come on!

210
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,410
‎-怎么了  ‎-快跑
-What's wrong? -Run!

211
00:23:57,500 --> 00:23:58,580
‎怎么了
What?

212
00:24:00,250 --> 00:24:01,120
‎趴下
Down!

213
00:24:15,330 --> 00:24:17,750
‎你怎么知道会爆炸
Ho-- how did you know it was gonna blow up?

214
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:19,200
‎炸弹就是会爆炸
Bombs tend to.

215
00:24:42,410 --> 00:24:44,000
抱歉 伙计
Sorry about that, buddy.

216
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,500
结果我还没做完
Turns out I'm not done yet.

217
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:48,620
‎炸弹 卢 ‎这说明他一直在计划这件事
A bomb? It means he's been plannin' this, Lou.

218
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:51,120
‎我们需要更多支援 我们得去找警长
We gotta get more help. We need to get to the sheriff.

219
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:53,500
‎没法去找他 没有车 电话也坏了
Can't get to him. No cars. Phones are down.

220
00:24:53,580 --> 00:24:55,040
‎我们在城外十几公里
We're ten miles outside of town.

221
00:24:55,120 --> 00:24:58,830
‎每耽误一秒 ‎你孩子就走远一步 我得去追踪他们
Your kid's gettin' further away by the second. I have to track 'em.

222
00:24:58,910 --> 00:24:59,830
‎什么
What?

223
00:25:00,330 --> 00:25:01,540
‎你追踪他们
Track 'em? You?

224
00:25:01,620 --> 00:25:03,290
‎去拿电池 在厨房
Get batteries. Kitchen.

225
00:25:09,450 --> 00:25:12,410
‎你不了解情况 菲利普以前当过兵
You don't understand. Philip was a Green Beret.

226
00:25:12,500 --> 00:25:15,870
‎他在中美洲做了可怕的事 ‎因此还被通缉了
Wanted for some terrible shit that he did in Central America.

227
00:25:16,450 --> 00:25:18,040
‎是战争罪什么的
War crimes kind of shit.

228
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:21,450
‎我看了法庭手稿 他折磨俘虏来作乐
I saw the court transcripts. He was torturing hostages for fun.

229
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:22,790
‎他训练有素
He's highly trained.

230
00:25:22,870 --> 00:25:26,080
‎是个炸弹专家 ‎妈的 我们可不是他的对手
An explosives expert. Well, we're no match for him, Lou.

231
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:30,540
‎我们需要专业的救援 ‎光凭你和你家狗是不行的
We need professional help. You and the dog ain't gonna cut it.

232
00:25:33,250 --> 00:25:35,580
‎他从你的拖车里拿走了什么吗
Did he take anything from your trailer?

233
00:25:36,830 --> 00:25:39,870
‎拿走了小薇最喜欢的 ‎河马先生玩偶 还有一条毯子
Her-- her favorite stuffy, Mr. Hippo. -And a-- a blanket.

234
00:25:39,950 --> 00:25:41,450
‎他想让她舒服一点
-He wants her comfortable.

235
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,330
‎他只想让她保持安静
He wants her quiet.

236
00:25:52,080 --> 00:25:53,370
‎正在翻修
Renovations.

237
00:26:01,500 --> 00:26:04,700
‎警察试图逮捕他时 ‎他炸毁了自己的公寓
When they tried to arrest him, he blew his apartment up.

238
00:26:04,790 --> 00:26:07,870
‎警察也发了死亡证明 ‎他怎么可能还活着
They sent a death certificate. How the hell could he still be alive?

239
00:26:10,950 --> 00:26:13,120
‎氟烷 会让人昏睡的气体
Halothane. Sleeping gas.

240
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:15,910
‎你没被迷晕 算你走运
You're lucky it didn't knock you out.

241
00:26:26,540 --> 00:26:28,500
‎他用东西把她拉着走了
He's pullin' her in somethin'.

242
00:26:28,580 --> 00:26:31,700
‎他要是想带小薇离开岛 ‎事情就更复杂了
If he gets her off the island, this will get a lot messier.

243
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:33,750
‎飞机场和渡轮都关了
Airport and ferry are closed.

244
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:40,790
‎要坐私人游艇 他就得去海岸
Private vessel. He's headed to the coast.

245
00:26:40,870 --> 00:26:44,410
‎他有领先优势 ‎我得抓紧了 你待在这里
He's got a head start. I gotta move fast. Stay here.

246
00:26:44,410 --> 00:26:45,830
暴风雨过后  再进城
The storm clears, head into town.

247
00:26:45,910 --> 00:26:48,000
当你看到第一个房子时 就打电话给警长
First house you see, call the sheriff.

248
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:54,120
‎-喂 你要去哪里  ‎-去找我的孩子
-Hey, where are you goin'? -To find my child.

249
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,040
‎你不知道自己在做什么
You don't know what you're doing.

250
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:04,700
‎如果你拖慢我的速度 ‎我就把你扔下不管
If you slow me down, I will leave you behind.

251
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:08,080
‎贾克斯 继续走
Jax. Right on.

252
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:48,950
‎什么都看不到
You can't see shit.

253
00:27:49,040 --> 00:27:51,540
‎我们很接近了 正在穿过山脊
We're close. We're clearing the ridge.

254
00:27:51,620 --> 00:27:53,000
‎我们马上就到
We'll be there shortly.

255
00:27:53,080 --> 00:27:54,120
‎该死的一群白痴
-Fuckin' idiots.

256
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:18,080
‎不 没关系
No. No, no, no. It's okay.

257
00:28:18,660 --> 00:28:20,160
‎我知道好久没见了
I know it's been a while.

258
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,910
‎也许这能唤起你的记忆
Maybe this'll jog your memory.

259
00:28:25,330 --> 00:28:26,540
‎这个是教堂
Here's the church…

260
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,500
‎这是尖顶
Here's the steeple…

261
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:32,040
‎把它打开 然后是…
Open it up and…

262
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:35,120
‎是你
It's you.

263
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:38,040
‎对 是的 是我
Yes, it is. It's-- it's me.

264
00:28:38,870 --> 00:28:40,200
‎是我 宝贝
It's me, sweetie.

265
00:28:43,250 --> 00:28:45,000
‎你探完险回来了
You came back from your adventure.

266
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,200
‎没错
I sure did.

267
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:53,000
‎我还给你带了礼物呢
And… and I even brought you a present.

268
00:28:55,950 --> 00:28:57,580
‎是在宝藏堆里找到的吗
Is it part of the treasure?

269
00:28:58,450 --> 00:29:00,200
‎宝藏 对
Uh, treasure? Yeah!

270
00:29:00,750 --> 00:29:02,290
‎没错 当然是了
Yeah, it sure is.

271
00:29:02,370 --> 00:29:06,830
‎而且你和我要一起 ‎去一趟属于我们的探险
And… you and I are gonna go on our own adventure together.

272
00:29:06,910 --> 00:29:10,870
‎妈妈在哪儿 她跟我们一起去吗
Where's Mo-- Where's Mommy? Is she coming with us?

273
00:29:12,620 --> 00:29:15,000
‎对 她当然要去
Yeah, of course she is. Of course she is.

274
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:19,450
‎我给她留了纸条和提示 让她跟上来
I left her a note and some clues to follow us,

275
00:29:19,540 --> 00:29:22,200
‎她晚点会跟我们汇合的 好吗
and she's gonna meet up with us after, okay?

276
00:29:26,910 --> 00:29:28,000
‎别急嘛
Uh-- Whoa.

277
00:29:28,830 --> 00:29:30,000
‎你要说什么
What do you say?

278
00:29:31,290 --> 00:29:32,290
‎谢谢 爸爸
Thank you, Daddy.

279
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:35,910
‎好的
-Okay.

280
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,250
‎能收到吗
- Do you copy?

281
00:29:37,330 --> 00:29:38,910
‎收到 快上线 能听到吗
Come on. Get on radio. -Do you copy?

282
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,620
‎好吧 我还有一件事要处理
-All right, I've gotta do one more thing.

283
00:29:42,250 --> 00:29:44,660
‎然后你就要和我一起开始探险了
And then you and I are gonna start our adventure together.

284
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:47,700
‎所以你戴上这个 好了 就是这样
See, you put these on… All right, like that.

285
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,080
‎好吗
Okay?

286
00:30:57,330 --> 00:30:58,290
‎给你
Here.

287
00:31:42,120 --> 00:31:43,250
‎你看到什么了吗
You see anything?

288
00:31:50,250 --> 00:31:53,290
‎-你认识他们  ‎-托尼和格里 是菲利普的战友
-You know them? -Tony and Gerry. They served with Philip.

289
00:31:54,250 --> 00:31:56,790
‎-他们就跟菲利普一样狠毒 ‎-来吧
They're just as vicious as he is. Come on.

290
00:31:56,870 --> 00:32:00,870
‎趴下别动 你的外套就是一个活靶子
Stay down. Your jacket might as well have a target painted on it.

291
00:32:02,330 --> 00:32:03,370
‎我们等着
-We wait.

292
00:32:04,040 --> 00:32:05,830
‎万一这只是声东击西呢
Suppose this is just a distraction?

293
00:32:05,910 --> 00:32:09,540
‎好争取更多时间让他带着小薇离开 ‎他就喜欢搞这种鬼把戏
Buying him more time to get away with Vee. It's the kind of game he likes to play.

294
00:32:09,620 --> 00:32:11,500
‎拿闪亮的东西在你面前晃
Danglin' somethin' shiny in front of you,

295
00:32:11,580 --> 00:32:14,830
‎然后他趁你不备 给你脑袋一闷棍
and you don't notice when he's about to bash you over your goddamn head.

296
00:32:20,830 --> 00:32:22,500
‎你会用枪吗
Do you know how to use this?

297
00:32:23,450 --> 00:32:26,750
‎我会 我离开他之后去上课学过
Mmm, yeah. -I took lessons after I left him.

298
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:28,870
‎好的 我得去看一下
-All right, I'm gonna go have a look.

299
00:32:28,950 --> 00:32:32,000
‎如果有人离得太近 就用这个
If anybody gets too close, use this.

300
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:35,000
‎直接戳眼睛 眼瞎的人没法要你的命
Go for the eyes. A man can't kill what he can't see.

301
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:39,370
‎-你在哪里学的这些东西  ‎-女童子军
-How do you know all this? -Girl Scouts.

302
00:32:40,910 --> 00:32:42,450
‎贾克斯 待着别动
Jax. Stay.

303
00:33:06,410 --> 00:33:08,790
‎这种鬼天气 没人想跟着他过来
All right, no one's gonna follow him in this shit.

304
00:33:10,290 --> 00:33:13,540
‎感觉这又是一次菲利普的蹩脚游戏
I'm telling you, this feels like another one of Philip's fucked-up games.

305
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,370
‎有人吗
Hello?

306
00:33:37,080 --> 00:33:41,250
‎不好意思 我把这里都转了个遍
Oh, excuse me. I'm completely turned around out here. I--

307
00:33:41,330 --> 00:33:44,120
‎我在找我家的狗 可怜的小家伙…
I… I was looking for my dog. The poor little guy--

308
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:46,580
‎-我没看到狗 ‎-好吧
I haven't seen any dogs. Okay.

309
00:33:47,120 --> 00:33:49,370
‎你有电话可以借给我用吗 我只想…
Do… do you have a phone I could use? -I just want--

310
00:33:49,450 --> 00:33:50,370
‎就你一个人
-Are you alone?

311
00:33:51,620 --> 00:33:52,790
‎很不幸 是的
Unfortunately. Um…

312
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:04,370
‎听我说 我感觉自己 ‎没法再撑三个小时走路回家了
Look, I-- I don't think I can make it the three hours back home, but…

313
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:09,620
‎不过 要是能歇歇脚就好了
if I could just rest and get my… my bearings?

314
00:34:15,330 --> 00:34:16,500
‎天啊
Christ.

315
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:20,080
‎好吧 只能待两分钟
-Okay. Just two minutes.

316
00:34:21,330 --> 00:34:22,660
‎非常感谢
Thank you so much.

317
00:34:22,750 --> 00:34:23,910
‎该死
Oh shit.

318
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,410
‎多谢你的善心
Oh, bless your heart.

319
00:34:29,370 --> 00:34:30,790
‎早上好啊
Oh, good morning.

320
00:34:30,870 --> 00:34:32,790
‎她的狗跑丢了 被雨淋湿了
She lost her dog, man. She's soaked.

321
00:34:32,870 --> 00:34:35,160
‎只要让我的血液循环起来就好
Just need to get my blood movin' again.

322
00:34:35,250 --> 00:34:37,330
‎天啊 外面的风暴真是厉害
My goodness. Quite a storm out there.

323
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:46,750
‎你叫什么名字
What's your name?

324
00:34:46,830 --> 00:34:48,500
‎哦 抱歉 我叫玛莎
Oh, sorry, I'm-- I'm Martha.

325
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,000
‎弗莱明
Flemming.

326
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:52,830
‎但你们可能认识我丈夫 ‎他上班的地方在…
But you might know my husband, Gordon. -He works at the--

327
00:34:52,910 --> 00:34:53,790
‎不认识
-I don't.

328
00:34:58,450 --> 00:35:00,700
‎来 坐一下吧
Here. Why don't you grab a seat?

329
00:35:00,790 --> 00:35:04,000
‎-让冰冷的脚休息一下 ‎-那就太好了
-Give those cold feet a break. -They sure could use it.

330
00:35:04,830 --> 00:35:05,790
‎谢谢
Thank you.

331
00:35:13,910 --> 00:35:15,000
‎非常感谢
Thank you so much.

332
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:22,250
‎你在岛上待了很久吗
So… been on this island long?

333
00:35:22,330 --> 00:35:24,330
‎32年了
-Oh, 32 years.

334
00:35:24,410 --> 00:35:25,750
‎不知道这有什么好的
-I don't get the appeal.

335
00:35:25,830 --> 00:35:28,080
‎过来一趟也麻烦 天气又糟糕
It's a pain in the ass to get to. -Weather's shit.

336
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:30,870
‎得慢慢习惯才行
