01:01:08,160 --> 01:01:09,620
-该死 -我是兰金‎警长
-God damn it. -This is Sheriff Rankin.

521
01:01:09,700 --> 01:01:10,950
你是谁 结束
Who is this? Over.

522
01:01:11,120 --> 01:01:13,450
‎警长 兰金警长
Sheriff! Sheriff Rankin.

523
01:01:14,950 --> 01:01:16,250
这是--这是汉娜·道森
This is-- this is Hannah Dawson.

524
01:01:18,120 --> 01:01:20,410
‎-…被绑架了 ‎-绑架
…kidnapped. Kidnapped?

525
01:01:23,250 --> 01:01:24,370
汉娜 你能听到我说话吗
Hannah, can you hear me?

526
01:01:24,450 --> 01:01:25,830
请重复一遍好吗
Can you repeat that, please?

527
01:01:25,910 --> 01:01:27,250
好的
Uh-- Okay.

528
01:01:27,330 --> 01:01:29,700
我女儿被她父亲绑架了
My daughter was kidnapped by her father.

529
01:01:29,790 --> 01:01:32,250
我...
I'm…

530
01:01:32,250 --> 01:01:35,200
‎-卢阿德尔和我在一起 ‎-汉娜 你能确认情况吗
Lou Adell is with me… Hannah, can you please confirm?

531
01:01:35,290 --> 01:01:38,160
‎-汉娜道森 你能听到吗  ‎-什么
Hannah Dawson? Can you hear me? What?

532
01:01:38,700 --> 01:01:40,120
‎你再说一次好吗
Say that… say that again?

533
01:01:40,200 --> 01:01:41,660
‎拜托
-Come on, come on, come on.

534
01:01:41,750 --> 01:01:42,910
‎警长
Sheriff?

535
01:01:44,870 --> 01:01:46,700
‎该死 好吧
Oh fuck. Okay…

536
01:01:47,750 --> 01:01:48,700
‎可恶
Shit.

537
01:01:50,500 --> 01:01:51,540
‎呼叫托瑞斯
Torres, come in.

538
01:01:53,080 --> 01:01:55,580
‎-警长 请讲 ‎-听着 我们有情况
-Go, Sheriff. -Listen, we got a situation.

539
01:01:56,080 --> 01:01:57,370
‎听起来难以置信
This is gonna sound a bit crazy,

540
01:01:57,450 --> 01:02:02,250
‎但是我想汉娜道森的女儿 ‎被她父亲绑架了
but I think Hannah Dawson's daughter has been kidnapped by… by her father.

541
01:02:03,250 --> 01:02:04,200
‎什么
What?

542
01:02:05,040 --> 01:02:08,700
‎听着 我们马上把信息发布出去
Listen, let's put it on the wire, right away,

543
01:02:08,790 --> 01:02:10,750
‎以防女孩被带离这座岛
in case she's taken off the island.

544
01:02:11,250 --> 01:02:16,160
‎好吧 汉娜道森 薇道森和卢阿德尔 ‎她好像也提到了卢
Okay? Hannah and Vee Dawson and Lou Adell. I think she mentioned Lou.

545
01:03:50,200 --> 01:03:51,200
‎放下枪
The guns.

546
01:03:52,000 --> 01:03:53,000
‎慢点
Slowly.

547
01:04:29,500 --> 01:04:30,370
‎你好 菲利普
Hello, Philip.

548
01:04:34,830 --> 01:04:36,080
‎别担心她
Don't worry about her.

549
01:04:36,910 --> 01:04:39,200
‎我已经确保她会保持昏睡
I've made sure she'll sleep through this.

550
01:04:39,830 --> 01:04:42,290
‎告诉我一件事 老实回答
Just tell me one thing. And be honest here.

551
01:04:43,700 --> 01:04:45,160
‎你为什么要出卖我
Why'd you sell me out?

552
01:04:48,790 --> 01:04:51,750
‎我知道你迟早会找到汉娜和小薇
I knew you'd track down Hannah and Vee sooner or later.

553
01:04:51,830 --> 01:04:53,660
‎我无法永远保护她们
I wasn't gonna be able to protect them forever.

554
01:04:53,750 --> 01:04:56,870
‎保护她们 这一切都是因你而起
Protect them? All of this is happening because of you.

555
01:04:58,370 --> 01:05:01,700
‎不是吗 汉娜可能太天真了 ‎她没想明白 但是我不傻
Okay? And Hannah may be too naive to-- to see it, but I don't.

556
01:05:01,790 --> 01:05:03,330
‎汉娜不知道我是谁
Hannah doesn't know who I am.

557
01:05:10,660 --> 01:05:12,700
‎你连承认我是你儿子都还做不到
You still can't even admit I'm your son.

558
01:05:19,000 --> 01:05:22,160
‎菲利普 你打算做什么  ‎为什么要这样你追我赶
So what's the plan, Philip? Why the elaborate chase?

559
01:05:22,250 --> 01:05:24,700
‎为什么要让我们追踪你  ‎你并不想伤害你的孩子
Why let us track you? You don't wanna hurt your kid.

560
01:05:24,790 --> 01:05:28,700
‎你知道吗 那些人把我掳走时 ‎我年纪就跟小薇一样
Did you know that Vee is the same age as I was when those-- those men took me?

561
01:05:30,040 --> 01:05:35,160
‎是的 但他们就没有 ‎像我现在这样 对她这么温柔了
Yeah, but they weren't as nice as, uh… as I'm being to her.

562
01:05:36,790 --> 01:05:39,950
‎这样的相似程度 你不觉得很巧吗
Can you appreciate that? The symmetry of that?

563
01:05:42,290 --> 01:05:44,700
‎我以为我妈妈也会回来救我
I thought my mommy was comin' back to save me, too.

564
01:05:44,790 --> 01:05:48,450
‎那是个陷阱 ‎要是我来救你的话 我俩都会被抓
It was a trap. If I'd tried to save you, they would have had us both.

565
01:05:48,540 --> 01:05:50,370
‎胡说 你只想保护自己的卧底身份
Bullshit. You wanted to maintain your cover.

566
01:05:50,450 --> 01:05:52,620
‎我只是你执行任务的一枚棋子而已
I was a pawn for your mission. Nothin' else.

567
01:05:52,700 --> 01:05:55,410
‎我救了你 我把你从伊朗救了出来
-I had you rescued. I got you out of Iran.

568
01:05:55,500 --> 01:05:58,410
‎那你怎么不跟我一起回来  ‎原因很简单
-Then why didn't you come back with me? Here's why.

569
01:05:59,120 --> 01:06:02,870
‎因为你他妈的选择了中情局 ‎而不是选择自己的孩子
Because you chose the fucking CIA over your own child.

570
01:06:04,080 --> 01:06:05,750
‎后来事情怎么样
Yeah, how'd that work out for you? Hmm?

571
01:06:07,250 --> 01:06:09,950
‎伊朗被你们搞得一团糟 ‎你们还做过比这更糟糕的事吗
I mean, did you guys fuck up anything worse than you fucked up Iran?

572
01:06:11,540 --> 01:06:14,410
‎然后 你偷走了我的妻子和孩子…
And then you steal my wife and-- and my kid--

573
01:06:14,500 --> 01:06:17,410
‎她们跟我犯的错无关 别牵扯上她们
Hannah and Vee had nothing to do with my mistakes. Leave them out of this.

574
01:06:17,500 --> 01:06:19,580
‎你就别给我上思想道德课了
Oh, spare me the fuckin' morality lesson.

575
01:06:19,660 --> 01:06:21,700
‎你早就放弃了这个权利
You gave up that right a long time ago.

576
01:06:24,500 --> 01:06:25,700
‎现在还不迟
It's not too late.

577
01:06:27,660 --> 01:06:29,790
‎你敢动一下 我就给你一枪
You move, I'mma put a bullet in you.

578
01:06:31,330 --> 01:06:32,540
‎现在还不迟
It's not too late.

579
01:06:33,330 --> 01:06:35,500
‎把小薇留给我 然后你走吧
Leave Vee with me and go.

580
01:06:36,620 --> 01:06:38,450
‎我会把她们从你的踪迹中抹去
I'll throw them off your trail.

581
01:06:39,950 --> 01:06:41,870
‎菲利普 听我说
Philip, listen to me.

582
01:06:41,950 --> 01:06:43,000
‎你说得对
You're right.

583
01:06:43,790 --> 01:06:47,200
‎你小时候我没保护好你 ‎现在就让我做弥补吧
I didn't protect you when you were a kid. So let me do it now.

584
01:06:48,910 --> 01:06:49,830
‎闭嘴
Shut up.

585
01:06:49,910 --> 01:06:51,410
‎怎么 你想杀我
What, you wanna kill me?

586
01:06:52,540 --> 01:06:53,450
‎动手吧
Do it.

587
01:06:55,040 --> 01:06:58,250
‎你昨晚带走小薇时 ‎我正拿着来复枪抵着自己脑袋
Before I knew you took Vee last night, I had my rifle pressed against my head.

588
01:06:58,330 --> 01:06:59,410
‎我不怕死
I'm not afraid to go.

589
01:07:01,910 --> 01:07:04,040
‎你别总是打乱我的思绪 好吗
You just can't stop messin' with my head, can't you?

590
01:07:04,120 --> 01:07:05,830
‎我甚至不知道从何讲起
Kid, I wouldn't even know where to start.

591
01:07:07,250 --> 01:07:10,080
‎我知道你把自己炸死了之后 ‎我就知道时机到了
The minute I heard you blew yourself up, I knew it was time.

592
01:07:10,160 --> 01:07:13,200
‎我以为汉娜和小薇会很安全 ‎我的任务已经完成了
I thought Hannah and Vee were safe. My mission was complete.

593
01:07:13,290 --> 01:07:14,750
‎但你欺骗了我
But you tricked me there, didn't you?

594
01:07:16,500 --> 01:07:18,200
‎你向来都比我聪明
You always were smarter than me.

595
01:07:21,250 --> 01:07:23,620
‎你五岁时下象棋就比我厉害很多
Beat my ass at chess when you were five years old.

596
01:07:26,330 --> 01:07:27,290
‎记得吗
Remember that?

597
01:07:30,330 --> 01:07:31,250
‎我记得
I do.

598
01:07:37,410 --> 01:07:38,660
‎哦 菲利普
Oh, Philip.

599
01:07:40,580 --> 01:07:41,540
‎你猜怎么着
You know what?

600
01:07:45,250 --> 01:07:48,200
‎这次要按我的游戏规则来玩
For once, we're playin' my game.

601
01:07:59,330 --> 01:08:01,200
‎是时候做个了结了
It's time to end this legacy.

602
01:08:01,290 --> 01:08:03,950
‎好让这一家子都摆脱痛苦
Put this whole family out of its misery.

603
01:08:07,290 --> 01:08:10,120
‎菲利普 你是她爸爸
Philip, you're her father.

604
01:08:10,200 --> 01:08:12,160
‎你也是我妈妈啊
And you're my mother.

605
01:09:33,080 --> 01:09:34,450
‎妈妈
Mom! Mom!

606
01:09:37,120 --> 01:09:39,950
‎我们会在灯塔等你
We'll be waiting for you at the lighthouse.

607
01:09:40,580 --> 01:09:42,410
‎一定要带汉娜一起来
Make sure you bring Hannah.

608
01:09:42,500 --> 01:09:43,700
‎别让我们久等
Don't take too long.

609
01:09:48,830 --> 01:09:49,790
‎妈的
Fuck.

610
01:09:58,790 --> 01:10:01,290
‎只是想问问你情况怎么样
Just checking in on ya. How are you doing out there?

611
01:10:01,790 --> 01:10:02,790
‎副警长 进展如何
-Talk to me, Deputy.

612
01:10:02,870 --> 01:10:04,370
‎在全境通缉布告里没找到匹配
-Still no hits on the APBs.

613
01:10:04,450 --> 01:10:07,750
‎已把卡车上的炸弹告知了交通运输部 ‎跟验尸官汇报了尸体情况
I notified ATF about the bomb in the truck and the coroner about the body.

614
01:10:07,830 --> 01:10:10,250
‎等天气好转 他们就会派队伍过来
They're sending teams when the weather lets up.

615
01:10:13,700 --> 01:10:15,620
‎奥卡斯岛警察局
Orcas Island Sheriff's Department.

616
01:10:15,700 --> 01:10:16,700
‎是的 长官
Yes, sir.

617
01:10:16,790 --> 01:10:19,250
‎警长 是联邦执法官
Sheriff, it's the federal marshals.

618
01:10:21,950 --> 01:10:23,200
‎我是兰金 你是哪位
-This is Rankin. Who's this?

619
01:10:23,290 --> 01:10:26,660
‎警长 我是多米尼克科朗 ‎你收到传真了吗
-Sheriff, Dominick Crown here. Did you receive our facsimile transmission?

620
01:10:26,750 --> 01:10:28,450
‎收到了 我正拿在手里
Yeah, I got it right here.

621
01:10:28,540 --> 01:10:31,870
‎我们在全境通缉布告里 ‎看到了你们所说的卢阿德尔
We've seen the APB for the woman you know as Lou Adell.

622
01:10:31,950 --> 01:10:34,000
‎她跟照片里的这个人相匹配吗
Is she a match for the person in that photo?

623
01:10:34,080 --> 01:10:36,160
‎对 是啊 看起来像是她
Yeah. Yeah, it sure looks like her.

624
01:10:36,250 --> 01:10:39,080
‎-你能确信是她吗 警长  ‎-就是她
-How confident are you, Sheriff? It's her.

625
01:10:39,160 --> 01:10:40,700
‎那第二个人呢
-And the second individual?

626
01:10:42,080 --> 01:10:43,540
‎等一下
-Hang on one second.

627
01:10:43,620 --> 01:10:45,200
‎你认得他吗
Do you recognize him?

628
01:10:45,290 --> 01:10:48,200
‎不认得 你是说这家伙也牵涉其中
No. Are you telling me that this guy is involved?

629
01:10:48,290 --> 01:10:51,250
‎你知道这些人所处的位置吗
Do you have any intel on the location of these individuals?

630
01:10:51,330 --> 01:10:53,450
‎-他们是不是在一起  ‎-我不知道
-Are they together? Well, I don't know if they're together.

631
01:10:53,540 --> 01:10:57,250
‎我想他们要去老鹰湾 位于岛的西侧
What I believe is that they're headed to Eagle Bay, on the west side of our island.

632
01:10:57,330 --> 01:11:00,080
‎我们必须确保没有平民前往那附近
We need to make sure no civilians go anywhere near that location.

633
01:11:00,160 --> 01:11:01,950
‎设置路障 封锁该区域
Set up roadblocks and cordon the area.

634
01:11:02,040 --> 01:11:04,500
‎还有个被绑架的小女孩 ‎她妈妈也在那里
There's a kidnapped girl and her mother out there.

635
01:11:05,500 --> 01:11:07,080
‎-你等一会儿 ‎-什么
-Hold. -Excuse me?

636
01:11:08,910 --> 01:11:11,700
‎这混蛋居然让我等着 难以置信
Asshole put me on hold. Unbelievable.

637
01:11:13,790 --> 01:11:14,910
太他妈不可思议了
Un-fuckin'-believable.

638
01:11:15,000 --> 01:11:16,200
兰金警长
Sheriff Rankin?

639
01:11:16,200 --> 01:11:17,200
‎对 就是我
- Yeah, right here.

640
01:11:17,290 --> 01:11:19,830
‎那个男性逃犯是美国特种部队的
The male fugitive is US Army Special Forces,

641
01:11:19,910 --> 01:11:22,370
‎因多起谋杀平民案而被定罪
convicted in the murder of numerous civilians.

642
01:11:22,450 --> 01:11:25,750
‎那个女性是中情局的重点通缉目标
The female is a high-priority target for the CIA.

643
01:11:25,830 --> 01:11:27,450
‎中情局 卢阿德尔
The CIA? Lou Adell?

644
01:11:27,540 --> 01:11:31,000
‎这项调查现在由美国执法官负责
This investigation is now under the jurisdiction of the US Marshals.

645
01:11:31,080 --> 01:11:32,950
‎已获授权使用致命武力
Lethal force has been authorized.

646
01:11:33,040 --> 01:11:37,160
‎禁止任何人进入老鹰湾 ‎你们部门的人不准…
Do not allow any approach to Eagle Bay. -Not by your department, not--

647
01:11:37,250 --> 01:11:40,290
那里有一个被绑架的女孩和她的母亲
There-- there is a kidnapped girl and her mother out there.

648
01:11:40,450 --> 01:11:42,160
‎别干扰我们执行任务 警长
Stay out of our way, Sheriff.

649
01:11:51,870 --> 01:11:53,370
‎（急救箱）

650
01:11:53,450 --> 01:11:55,950
‎卢 抱歉 我来晚了
Lou, sorry it took me so long.

651
01:11:56,040 --> 01:11:59,160
‎我试着尽量往高处爬 但是…
I tried to get as high as I could, but…

652
01:11:59,950 --> 01:12:02,200
‎天啊 见鬼
-Jesus. Oh shit.

653
01:12:02,700 --> 01:12:05,580
‎天啊 好 等等 我来帮你
Oh God, oh God, oh God. Okay, wait, wait. Let me help. Let me help.

654
01:12:07,830 --> 01:12:08,950
‎是他干的吗
-Did he do this?

655
01:12:10,370 --> 01:12:12,330
‎小薇呢 她没事吧
And Vee? Is she… is she all right?

656
01:12:12,410 --> 01:12:16,540
‎她暂时没事 他把她带去灯塔了
She's okay for now. He's taking her to the lighthouse.

657
01:12:20,950 --> 01:12:22,080
‎动作要快
Do it quick--

658
01:12:26,500 --> 01:12:28,000
‎我正在弄
-I'm trying.

659
01:12:28,750 --> 01:12:31,200
‎尽量用纱布填满它
Fill it with gauze. As-- as much as you can.

660
01:12:34,580 --> 01:12:37,790
‎-该死 ‎-来吧 深入一点 把伤口包紧了
-Oh shit. -Come on, deeper. -Really pack it in.

661
01:12:37,870 --> 01:12:41,950
‎我正在弄 天啊 卢 ‎很抱歉 我把你拉下这趟浑水
-I'm trying. -Jesus, Lou. -I'm so sorry I dragged you into this.

662
01:12:42,660 --> 01:12:46,500
‎把手放在这里 用力按 我去拿些胶布
Put your hand here. Right. Press down. Okay, good. I gotta-- I gotta grab some tape.

663
01:12:47,620 --> 01:12:49,290
‎你联系上警长了吗
Hannah. Did you reach the sheriff?

664
01:12:49,370 --> 01:12:50,910
‎-我也不确定 ‎-先别管了
-Uh, I don't know. -Leave it.

665
01:12:51,000 --> 01:12:52,410
‎-等等 ‎-不用了
-Wait, uh-- -It's fine.

666
01:13:05,160 --> 01:13:07,620
‎是我在小屋里找到的 ‎我原本想告诉你的
I found those at the cabin. I meant to tell you.

667
01:13:10,790 --> 01:13:11,750
‎你在说谎
You're lying.

668
01:13:27,910 --> 01:13:29,790
‎（嗨 妈妈 轮到我啦）

669
01:13:36,330 --> 01:13:38,290
‎这个留言不是给我的 对吧
This message isn't for me, is it?

670
01:13:39,330 --> 01:13:40,370
‎都不是给我的
None of them are.

671
01:13:48,290 --> 01:13:49,200
‎你说吧
Say it.

672
01:13:51,250 --> 01:13:52,620
‎我要你亲口说出来
I need you to say it.

673
01:13:57,250 --> 01:13:58,200
‎说啊
Say it!

674
01:14:00,040 --> 01:14:02,790
‎他是我儿子
He's… my son.

675
01:14:09,540 --> 01:14:11,040
‎我之前驻扎在伊朗
When I was stationed in Iran,

676
01:14:11,120 --> 01:14:14,080
‎当时我必须接近一个极度危险的人物
I had to get close to a very dangerous man.

677
01:14:14,700 --> 01:14:15,790
‎关系很亲密
-Very close.

678
01:14:16,750 --> 01:14:17,910
‎不是吧
No, no, no, no.

679
01:14:20,000 --> 01:14:22,120
‎我留着孩子是为了掩护我的卧底身份
I kept the baby to keep my cover.

680
01:14:22,200 --> 01:14:25,950
