‎天啊 瞧瞧我
Jesus, look at me.

763
01:21:12,330 --> 01:21:15,450
‎这么多年了 我还在等我妈妈回来
Still waitin' for my mommy to come back after all these years, huh?

764
01:21:17,250 --> 01:21:19,830
‎但我们确实需要等她来 了结这件事
But we do need her here to finish this.

765
01:21:23,330 --> 01:21:25,580
‎我想给妈妈一个拥抱
I wanna give Mommy a hug.

766
01:21:35,580 --> 01:21:36,910
‎菲利普 拜托
Philip, please.

767
01:21:46,830 --> 01:21:48,000
‎求你了 爸爸
Please, Daddy?

768
01:21:49,040 --> 01:21:50,080
‎好的 小薇
Okay, Vee.

769
01:21:50,580 --> 01:21:52,870
‎反正我们也在等卢 那就抱一下吧
One quick hug while we wait for Lou.

770
01:21:55,370 --> 01:21:57,080
‎我好想你啊
Oh, I missed you so much.

771
01:22:09,950 --> 01:22:11,580
