‎爸爸 我能去洗手间吗
Daddy, may I go to the bathroom?

773
01:22:26,750 --> 01:22:28,200
‎当然可以 小薇
Of course you can, Vee.

774
01:22:28,830 --> 01:22:31,620
‎但是上完就立刻回来 好吗
But hey… Come right back, okay?

775
01:22:45,450 --> 01:22:47,330
‎哇 卢对你的影响真不小嘛
Wow, Lou is really rubbin' off on you.

776
01:22:49,450 --> 01:22:52,330
‎来 把枪给我 ‎我们都知道你不会开枪打我的
Come on, just give me the gun. We both know you're not gonna shoot me.

