‎尽量找一根最长的 去吧
The longest one you can find. Go, go, go.

851
01:32:18,910 --> 01:32:20,620
‎-妈妈  ‎-嘿 宝贝
-Mommy! -Hey, baby.

852
01:32:21,370 --> 01:32:22,750
‎汉娜 对讲机
Hannah. The radio.

853
01:32:23,370 --> 01:32:24,370
‎在我的口袋里
In my pocket.

854
01:32:25,250 --> 01:32:26,500
‎-来吧 ‎-帮帮我
-Come on. -Help me.

855
01:32:26,580 --> 01:32:27,950
‎快 快走
-All right. -Come on, go, run.

856
01:32:29,870 --> 01:32:31,950
‎汉娜 尽量把它举高点
Hannah, hold this up as high as you can.

857
01:32:34,000 --> 01:32:36,080
‎-你是在求救吗  ‎-对
-Are you calling for help? -Yeah.

858
01:32:43,790 --> 01:32:46,370
‎是的 这应该能引起他们的注意
Yeah. That ought to get their attention.

859
01:32:52,540 --> 01:32:53,500
‎你赶紧走
You gotta go.

860
01:32:53,580 --> 01:32:56,620
‎沿着这条路往镇上走 把贾克斯带上
Take the road back towards town.

861
01:32:56,620 --> 01:32:57,870
- 把贾克斯带来 - 你…你和我们一起来
-Bring Jax with you. -You… you come with us.

862
01:32:58,040 --> 01:33:00,080
‎汉娜你要照料好你的孩子
Hannah, you take care of your kid…

863
01:33:01,410 --> 01:33:02,500
‎而我会照料我的孩子
I'll take care of mine.

864
01:33:03,200 --> 01:33:06,290
‎我在家给你留了封信 一定要找到它
I left a letter for you at my house. Make sure you find it.

865
01:33:08,200 --> 01:33:09,250
‎走吧 小薇
Okay. Go on, Vee.

866
01:33:10,330 --> 01:33:11,410
‎可恶
Oh, God damn it.

867
01:33:15,700 --> 01:33:17,290
‎卢 你可别死了
Don't die on me now, Lou.

868
01:33:19,750 --> 01:33:22,160
‎你眼前的就是最重要的一切
Everything that matters is right here in front of you.

869
01:33:23,910 --> 01:33:24,870
‎我知道
I know.

870
01:33:26,410 --> 01:33:28,200
‎去吧 快点
Go. Now!

871
01:36:28,500 --> 01:36:29,620
‎对不起 孩子
I'm sorry, kid.

872
01:37:38,160 --> 01:37:39,910
‎-嘿 小薇 ‎-嘿
-Hey, Vee. -Hey.

873
01:37:40,540 --> 01:37:41,750
‎你好 贾克斯
Hello, Jax.

874
01:37:42,410 --> 01:37:44,580
‎嘿 你现在有两条手链了
Hey, you got two bracelets now.

875
01:37:45,200 --> 01:37:46,040
‎对
Yeah.

876
01:37:46,540 --> 01:37:47,750
‎就像你一样
Just like you.

877
01:37:47,830 --> 01:37:49,160
‎（卢）

878
01:37:49,870 --> 01:37:51,000
‎一条是为了纪念朋友
One's for a friend.

879
01:37:51,620 --> 01:37:54,620
‎她突然就把这房子给了你和你女儿
So, out of the blue, she just leaves you and your daughter this house?

880
01:37:55,370 --> 01:37:59,200
‎是的 这间房子还有很多冷冻鹿肉
Yeah, this house and a ton of frozen deer meat.

881
01:37:59,700 --> 01:38:00,700
‎门没锁
It's open.

882
01:38:01,620 --> 01:38:03,540
‎-嘿 汉娜 ‎-嘿
-Hey, Han. -Hey.

883
01:38:03,620 --> 01:38:04,620
‎你们好
Oh, hello.

884
01:38:07,910 --> 01:38:10,160
‎我们还有几个问题要问道森女士
We had a few more questions for Ms. Dawson here.

885
01:38:10,160 --> 01:38:12,290
希望我没有打扰你
I hope I'm not interrupting.

886
01:38:13,250 --> 01:38:16,330
‎汉娜 验尸官那边有个问题
Hannah, uh, coroner's got an issue.

887
01:38:16,410 --> 01:38:20,750
‎你是亲属 需要你签名 ‎才能给菲利普的遗体放行
You're next of kin. He needs a signature to release Philip's body for burial.

888
01:38:22,160 --> 01:38:23,160
‎抱歉
-Yeah. Sorry.

889
01:38:25,700 --> 01:38:28,540
‎道森女士 卢阿德尔跟你提起过
Ms. Dawson, did Lou Adell ever mention

890
01:38:28,620 --> 01:38:30,750
‎她在中情局任职期间的文件吗
anything about documents from her time in the CIA to you?

891
01:38:31,330 --> 01:38:33,580
‎要是提起过 她这特务就太菜了
She'd be a pretty shit spy if she did.

892
01:38:36,950 --> 01:38:38,250
‎如果你想起任何线索…
If you think of anything…

893
01:38:39,200 --> 01:38:42,410
‎你上次和上上次来的时候给过名片了
You gave me a card last time you were here, and the time before that.

894
01:38:42,500 --> 01:38:43,750
‎任何线索都行
Anything at all.

895
01:38:45,500 --> 01:38:46,540
‎好吧
All right.

896
01:38:51,290 --> 01:38:53,410
‎-警长 告辞 ‎-很高兴又见到你
-Sheriff. -Good to see you again.

897
01:39:01,080 --> 01:39:01,910
‎别管他们
-Forget them.

898
01:39:02,700 --> 01:39:05,250
‎看来你们俩准备好去西雅图了
Looks like you two are ready for Seattle.

899
01:39:05,330 --> 01:39:06,950
‎你都收拾好了
Yeah, you're all packed up.

900
01:39:07,040 --> 01:39:08,330
‎对 差不多
Yeah, almost.

901
01:39:08,410 --> 01:39:11,660
‎我想告诉你 追悼会办得很体面
I wanted to tell you, you just did a beautiful job with the memorial service.

902
01:39:11,700 --> 01:39:12,540
打住  不  是你干的
-Stop. -No, you did.

903
01:39:12,620 --> 01:39:14,620
我想卢会很感激的
And I think Lou would have really appreciated it.

904
01:39:15,330 --> 01:39:19,120
‎得了吧 那些真情吐露只会让她作呕
Come on now. All that sincere emotion would have made her puke.

905
01:39:21,830 --> 01:39:23,160
‎她这人吧…
Oh, well…

906
01:39:25,500 --> 01:39:26,950
‎她确实很有个性
-She was her own person.

907
01:39:27,870 --> 01:39:31,910
‎我是说 有时候我很生她的气 但是
I mean, sometimes, I'm just so damn mad at her, and then…

908
01:39:33,750 --> 01:39:35,450
‎有时候又很想念她
Other times I miss her.

909
01:39:36,660 --> 01:39:38,910
‎对家人的感情不都是这样的吗
Isn't that just how it is with family?

910
01:39:45,620 --> 01:39:49,410
‎我向来不是话多的人 ‎我就长话短说了
"I've never been one for many words, so I'll keep this short."

911
01:39:53,120 --> 01:39:55,500
‎房子归你了 拿去卖掉吧
"The house is yours. Sell it."

912
01:39:56,290 --> 01:40:00,410
‎冰箱的肉够贾克斯吃一个月 ‎还有给你一些现金
"There's a month's worth of meat for Jax in the freezer, and some cash for you."

913
01:40:04,910 --> 01:40:09,620
‎人生没有二次机会 ‎但有时候它允许你重新开始
"Life doesn't give you second chances, but sometimes it does offer a fresh start."

914
01:40:17,040 --> 01:40:21,700
‎汉娜 你会好奇我为什么这么做 ‎为什么把这一切留给你
"Hannah, you're going to wonder why I did it." "Why I left this all for you."

915
01:40:23,500 --> 01:40:24,950
‎简单来说
"The simple answer is,

916
01:40:26,450 --> 01:40:29,450
‎你留给这个世界的东西 ‎会比我留下的东西更美好
you'll leave the world a better place than I did."

917
01:47:23,580 --> 01:47:28,580
‎字幕翻译：杨宇航


